in%201969%20as%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Arthur%20Rock%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20He%20was%20captivated%20by%20innovation%20and%20entrepreneurship%20and%20eager%20to%20help%20shape%20the%20nascent%20venture%20capital%20industry.%20When%20he%20co-founded%20NEA%20with%20Chuck%20Newhall%20and%20Frank%20Bonsal%20in%201977%2C%20the%20trio%20set%20out%20to%20form%20a%20%26quot%3B100-year%20partnership%26quot%3B%E2%80%94an%20enduring%20institution%20that%20would%20span%20many%20funds%20and%20flourish%20long%20into%20the%20future%2C%20built%20upon%20shared%20goals%2C%20shared%20values%2C%20and%20shared%20rewards.%20That%20guiding%20principle%20would%20shape%20NEA's%20evolution%20and%20success%20not%20only%20during%20the%20co-founders'%20tenures%2C%20but%20through%20numerous%20successive%20leadership%20transitions%20in%20the%20decades%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Managing%20Partner%20for%20our%20first%20seven%20funds%20and%20a%20General%20Partner%20through%20NEA%2013%2C%20Dick%20was%20instrumental%20in%20many%20of%20NEA's%20most%20successful%20outcomes%20over%20many%20years.%20He%20led%20investments%20in%20seminal%20companies%20like%20Juniper%20Networks%2C%20Macromedia%2C%20Ascend%20Communications%2C%20Immunex%2C%20Xoom%2C%20Financial%20Engines%20and%20many%20others%3B%20he%20was%20also%20among%20the%20earliest%20investors%20in%20Apple.%20Yet%20the%20true%20magnitude%20of%20his%20impact%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20visionary%20leadership%2C%20his%20relentless%20curiosity%2C%20and%20his%20hallmark%20tenacity.%20He%20was%20a%20true%20champion%20for%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20that%20long-term%20perspective%20combined%20with%20his%20stalwart%20conviction%20was%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20many%20of%20his%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDick%20once%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20think%20venture%20capital%20is%20a%20game%20of%20numbers.%20It's%20not%E2%80%94it's%20a%20game%20of%20courage.%26quot%3B%20That%20wisdom%20continues%20to%20resonate%20within%20our