0with%20friends.%20Last%20year%2C%20viewers%20watched%20over%20400%20million%20hours%20of%20podcasts%20monthly%20on%20living%20room%20devices%2C%20tuning%20into%20podcasts%20similar%20to%20a%20late-night%20talk%20show%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.youtube%2Fnews-and-events%2F2024-recap-of-youtube-on-tv%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20according%20to%20YouTube%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20want%20to%20watch%20their%20favorite%20podcasts%20in%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20living%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Chuk%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20sense.%20But%20that's%20certainly%20something%20we%20didn't%20expect%20three%20or%20four%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e6a70fa-5c6c-4875-8c5e-16b88d3536d8%5C%22%3EPodcasts%20open%20up%20more%20opportunities%20to%20make%20money%2C%20like%20with%20touring%20and%20merchandise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Cooper%20might%20be%20the%20best%20example%20of%20an%20influencer%20who's%20turned%20a%20podcast%20into%20a%20sprawling%20business%20empire.%20Cooper's%20podcast%20company%2C%20Unwell%20Network%2C%20offers%20several%20shows%2C%20and%20she%20recently%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcall-her-daddy-star-alex-cooper-launches-unwell-hydration-nestle-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20electrolyte%20drink%20called%20Unwell%20Hydration.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20average%20creator%2C%20there%20are%20several%20ways%20to%20monetize%20a%20podcast%2C%20from%20memberships%20and%20merchandise%20to%20live%20shows%20and%20brand%20deals.%20And%20the%20podcast%20format%20can%20open%20up%20more%20revenue%20streams%20than%20traditional%20YouTube%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20podcasts%20are%20typically%20over%20an%20hour%20long%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20an%20easy%20format%20for%20a%20live%20show%20or%20tour.%20The%20longer%20the%20podcast%2C%20the%20more%20advertisements%20a%20creator%20can%20place.%20Unlike