ed%20to%20bundle%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20in%20the%20short%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20media%20companies%20that%20have%20launched%20stand-alone%20streaming%20services%20should%20pivot%20hard%2C%20TD%20Cowen%20analysts%20argued%20in%20a%20recent%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20say%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%2C%20Disney%2C%20and%20Paramount%20should%20return%20to%20the%20wholesale%20business%20rather%20than%20continuing%20to%20build%20direct-to-consumer%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20overall%20vision%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmega-streaming%20bundle%26quot%3B%20distributed%20by%20Apple%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Google%2C%20or%20cable%20companies%20like%20Comcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone's%20producing%20more%20content%20than%20they%20used%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Doug%20Creutz%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20analyst%20at%20TD%20Cowen%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEveryone's%20advertising%20for%20their%20content%20more%20than%20they%20used%20to%2C%20and%20consumer%20dollars%20haven't%20increased%20that%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bundle%20would%20help%20players%20spread%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20content%20marketing%20and%20production.%20Creutz%20said%20he%20foresees%20a%20bundle%20happening%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBundling%20is%20the%20right%20way%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Wedbush%20Securities%20managing%20director%20Michael%20Pachter%20told%20BI%2C%20similarly%20predicting%20a%20three-year%20timeframe.%20Pachter%20said%20a%20bundle%20would%20aid%20content%20discovery%20in%20a%20fragmented%20content%20landscape%20and%20make%20subscriptions%20stickier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETD%20Cowen%20predicted%20that%20WBD%20and%20Disney%20would%20see%20single-digit%20DTC%20profitability%20in%202025%20and%20that%20Paramount%20and%20Comcast%20would%20reduce%20their%20DTC%20losses.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBut%20Creutz%20said%20the%20picture%20isn't%20improving%20enough%20to%20m