t%20Rich%20Greenfield%20noted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Netflix%20spokesperson%20pointed%20BI%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs22.q4cdn.com%2F959853165%2Ffiles%2Fdoc_financials%2F2024%2Fq3%2FFINAL-Q3-24-Shareholder-Letter.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQ3%20shareholder%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20said%20the%20breadth%20of%20its%20content%20made%20bundling%20unnecessary%20%E2%80%94%20unlike%20for%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20Netflix%20couldn't%20be%20impacted%20by%20a%20potential%20mega-bundle%2C%20however.%20Creutz%20said%20that%20while%20Netflix%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20advantage%26quot%3B%20competing%20against%20streamers%20individually%2C%20a%20mega-bundle%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20an%20obstacle%20to%20their%20path%20to%20world%20domination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Pachter%20said%20bundling%20could%20be%20welcomed%20by%20Netflix%20if%20the%20streamer%20could%20dictate%20the%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20is%20another%20company%20that%20complicates%20the%20picture.%20Creutz%20said%20the%20Mouse%20House%20harbors%20ambitions%20of%20being%20the%20last%20man%20standing%20with%20Netflix%2C%20and%20if%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fespn-ad-streaming-2025-flagship-venu-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estand-alone%20ESPN%20product%20succeeds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bthen%20I%20think%20their%20need%20for%20other%20people%20diminishes.%26quot%3B%20Disney%20also%20offers%20its%20own%20in-house%20bundle%20of%20Disney%2B%2C%20Hulu%2C%20and%20ESPN%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Disney%20has%20already%20shown%20a%20willingness%20to%20bundle%20with%20outside%20companies.%20It%20partnered%20with%20WBD%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-hulu-max-bundle-wbd-streaming-wars-data-analysis-strategy-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eservice%20that%20includes%20Disney%2B%2C%20Hulu%2C%20and%20Max%3C%2Fa%3E.