20Mexico%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20China%20that%20he%20says%20are%20meant%20to%20push%20them%20to%20do%20more%20to%20stop%20fentanyl%2C%20an%20addictive%20synthetic%20opioid%2C%20from%20entering%20the%20US.%20So%20far%2C%20it's%20prompted%20each%20country%20to%20announce%20potential%20countermeasures%2C%20with%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20promising%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-plan-deadline-trade-policies-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretaliatory%20moves%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20analysts'%20eyes%20are%20now%20on%20Cook%20to%20see%20whether%20he%20can%20successfully%20extricate%20Apple%20from%20the%20levies%20%E2%80%94%20like%20he%20managed%20to%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-apple-supply-chain-trump-tariffs-china-diversify-iphone-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20China%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20dealing%20with%20a%20new%20political%20and%20market%20landscape%2C%20and%20similar%20exemptions%20aren't%20guaranteed%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacob%20Bourne%2C%20tech%20analyst%20at%20EMARKETER%2C%20a%20Business%20Insider%20sister%20company%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20makes%20about%2095%25%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-dependent-on-china-economy-manufacturing-problem-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20popular%20products%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Forbes%20previously%20reported.%20Trump's%20added%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20the%20country's%20imports%20to%20the%20US%20would%20mean%20the%20cost%20could%20fall%20on%20consumers%20or%20the%20company%20itself%2C%20analysts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20Cook%20is%20already%20pursuing%20a%20workaround%20for%20Apple%2C%20but%20Morningstar%20analyst%20William%20Kerwin%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-making-apple-iphone-chips-helps-us-semiconduc