Likely%20To%20Visit%20US%20On%20February%2012%2C%20Hold%20Talks%20With%20Trump%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20likely%20to%20visit%20the%20US%20on%20February%2012%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said.%20This%20would%20be%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20historic%20comeback%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20travel%20plan%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20fly%20to%20Washington%20DC%20after%20his%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Paris%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20there%20is%20no%20official%20announcement%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20be%20among%20a%20handful%20of%20foreign%20leaders%20to%20travel%20to%20Washington%20DC%20on%20a%20bilateral%20visit%20within%20weeks%20after%20the%20Trump%20administration%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20is%20travelling%20to%20Paris%20to%20attend%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Action%20summit%20on%20February%2010%20and%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20PM%20Modi%20goes%20to%20the%20US%2C%20it%20would%20be%20amid%20concerns%20in%20India%20over%20Donald%20Trump's%20approach%20on%20immigration%20and%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20on%20Sunday%20announced%20imposing%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20imports%20as%20well%20as%20an%20additional%2010%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20Chinese%20goods.%20Later%2C%20he%20put%20a%20hold%20tariff%20on%20Mexican%20imports%2C%20but%20did%20not%20announce%20any%20relief%20for%20the%20other%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20phone%20call%20on%20January%2027%2C%20a%20week%20after%20the%20new%20US%20President's%20inauguration%2C%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20agreed%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20%26quot%3Btrusted%26quot%3B%20partnership%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20boosting%20India-US%20cooperation%20in%20trade%2C%20energy%20and%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20phone%20talks%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20Donald%20Trump%20emphasised%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20India%20increasing%20its%20procurement%20of%20US-made%20security%20equipment%20and%20moving%20toward%20a%20fair%20bilateral%20trade%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20already%20indicated%20its%20keenness%20to%20expand%20energy%20ties%20with%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20clean%20energy%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Saturday%20announced%20plans%20to%20amend%20its%20nuclear%20liability%20law%20and%20set%20up%20a%20nuclear%20energy%20mission%2C%20a%20move%20that%20came%20ahead%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20likely%20visit%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertain%20clauses%20in%20India's%20Civil%20Liability%20for%20Nuclear%20Damage%20Act%2C%202010%20have%20emerged%20as%20hurdles%20in%20moving%20forward%20in%20implementing%20the%20historic%20civil%20nuclear%20deal%20that%20was%20firmed%20up%20between%20the%20countries%2016%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20said%20to%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20civil%20nuclear%20cooperation%20with%20the%20US%20in%20small%20modular%20reactors%20(SMRs).%20US-based%20Holtec%20International%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20exporters%20of%20SMRs%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20is%20learnt%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20collaborating%20with%20the%20American%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738607940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9pufioj_pm-modi-trump-afp_650x400_27_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-likely-to-visit-us-on-february-12-hold-talks-with-donald-trump-say-sources-7627377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20likely%20to%20visit%20the%20US%20on%20February%2012%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20