514.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Premier%20Energies%20halts%20US%20solar%20cell%20facility%20plans%20amid%20policy%20uncertainty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738594842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpremier-energies-halts-us-solar-cell-facility-plans-amid-policy-uncertainty-125020301129_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Concerns%20over%20US%20stance%20on%20clean%20energy%20have%20weighed%20on%20shares%20of%20Premier%2C%20which%20have%20lost%20about%2023%25%20since%20hitting%20a%20peak%20in%20December%2C%20after%20listing%20in%20September%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpremier-energies-halts-us-solar-cell-facility-plans-amid-policy-uncertainty-125020301129_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Proposal%20To%20Increase%20Working%20Hours%20To%2070%20or%2090%20Hours%20Per%20Week%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20on%20Monday%20told%20Parliament%20that%20it%20is%20not%20considering%20any%20proposal%20to%20increase%20the%20maximum%20working%20hours%20to%2070%20or%2090%20hours%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20some%20of%20the%20corporate%20leaders%20proposed%20to%20increase%20the%20maximum%20working%20hours%20to%2070%20and%20even%2090%20hours%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20such%20proposal%20to%20increase%20the%20maximum%20working%20hours%20to%2070%20or%2090%20hours%20a%20week%20is%20under%20consideration%20of%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Labour%20%26amp%3B%20Employment%20Shobha%20Karandlaje%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20informed%20the%20House%20that%20labour%20being%20a%20subject%20under%20the%20Concurrent%20List%2C%20the%20enforcement%20of%20labour%20laws%20is%20done%20by%20state%20governments%20and%20the%20central%20government%20in%20their%20respective%20jurisdictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20the%20Central%20sphere%2C%20the%20enforcement%20is%20done%20through%20the%20inspecting%20officers%20of%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Relations%20Machinery%20(CIRM)%2C%20the%20compliance%20in%20the%20states%20is%20ensured%20through%20their%20labour%20enforcement%20machineries%2C%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20existing%20labour%20laws%2C%20working%20conditions%2C%20including%20working%20hours%20and%20overtime%2C%20are%20regulated%20through%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Factories%20Act%201948%20and%20the%20Shops%20and%20Establishments%20Acts%20of%20the%20respective%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20establishments%2C%20including%20the%20corporate%20sector%2C%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20Shops%20and%20Establishments%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20discourse%20over%2070-90-hour%20work%20week%2C%20pre-Budget%20Economic%20Survey%20on%20Friday%20last%20had%20cited%20studies%20to%20state%20that%20spending%20over%2060%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20work%20could%20have%20adverse%20health%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20noted%20that%20spending%20long%20hours%20at%20one's%20desk%20is%20detrimental%20to%20mental%20well-being%2C%20and%20individuals%20who%20spend%2012%20or%20more%20hours%20(per%20day)%20at%20a%20desk%20have%20distressed%20or%20struggling%20levels%20of%20mental%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20hours%20spent%20at%20work%20are%20informally%20considered%20a%20measure%20of%20productivity%2C%20a%20previous%20study%20has%20documented%20adverse%20health%20effects%20when%20hours%20exceed%2055-60%20per%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20survey%20said%2C%20citing%20findings%20by%20Pega%20F%20Nafradi%20B%20(2021)%20and%20'A%20systematic%20analysis%20from%20the%20WHO%2FILO%20Joint%20Estimates%20of%20the%20Work-related%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20and%20Injury'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20data%20from%20a%20study%20done%20by%20Sapien%20Labs%20Centre%20for%20Human%20Brain%20and%20Mind%2C%20the%20economic%20survey%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSpending%20long%20hours%20at%20one's%20desk%20is%20equally%20detrimental%20to%20mental%20well-being.%20Individuals%20who%20spend%2012%20or%20more%20hours%20at%20a%20desk%20have%20distressed%2F%20struggling%20levels%20of%20mental%20well-being%2C%20with%20a%20mental%20well-being%20score%20approximately%20100%20points%20lower%20than%20those%20who%20spend%20less%20than%20or%20equal%20to%20two%20hours%20at%20a%20desk%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20study%20by%20WHO%2C%20the%20survey%20said%20globally%2C%20about%2012%20billion%20days%20are%20lost%20annually%20due%20to%20depression%20and%20anxiety%2C%20amounting%20to%20a%20financial%20loss%20of%20USD%201%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20rupee%20terms%2C%20this%20translates%20to%20about%20Rs%207%2C000%20per%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20take%20by%20the%20Economic%20Survey%202024-25%20on%20work%20hour%20week%20had%20come%20weeks%20after%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20Ltd%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%20sparked%20off%20a%20raging%20debate%20on%20social%20media%20when%20he%20said%20employees%20should%20work%2090-hour%20a%20week%2C%20including%20on%20Sundays%20rather%20than%20sit%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20followed%20Infosys%20co-founder%20Narayana%20Murthy's%20suggestion%20of%20a%2070-hour%20workweek%20and%20Adani%20Group%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani's%20%26quot%3Bbiwi%20bhaag%20jayegi%20(wife%20will%20run%20away)%26quot%3B%20remark%20if%20one%20spent%20more%20than%20eight%20hours%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Subrahmanyan%20drew%20criticism%20from%20some%20peers%20in%20the%20business%20community.%20RPG%20Group%20Chairman%20Harsh%20Goenka%20said%20longer%20working%20hours%20was%20a%20recipe%20for%20burnout%20and%20not%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahindra%20Group%20Chairman%20Anand%20Mahindra%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20work%20and%20productivity%20rather%20than%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20spent%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20ITC%20Ltd%20Chairman%20Sanjiv%20Puri%20stated%20that%20empowering%20employees%20to%20realise%20their%20potential%20and%20accomplish%20their%20jobs%20well%20was%20more%20important%20than%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20put%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work-life%20balance%20debate%20echoes%20a%20similar%20one%20in%20China%20where%20the%20so-called%20'996%20culture'%20-%20the%20three%20digits%20describe%20a%20punishing%20schedule%20of%209%20am%20to%209%20pm%20six%20days%20a%20week%20-%20is%20being%20hotly%20debated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738594680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9oo119t_officerepresentativeimage_625x300_06_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-proposal-to-increase-working-hours-to-70-or-90-hours-per-week-centre-7626012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20on%20Monday%20told%20Parliament%20that%20it%20is%20not%20considering%20any%20proposal%20to%20increase%20the%20maximum%20working%20hours%20to%2070%20or%2090%20hours%20a%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-proposal-to-increase-working-hours-to-70-or-90-hours-per-week-centre-7626012%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt's%20High%20Time...%26quot%3B%3A%20R%20Ashwin's%20Brutal%20Analysis%20Of%20SKY%2C%20Samson's%20Poor%20Form%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A