0I%20can%20understand%20it%20happening%20in%20one%20or%20two%20games%2C%20but%20this%20is%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20know%20a%20tactic%20is%20being%20used%20against%20you%2C%20it%20becomes%20your%20responsibility%20to%20find%20a%20new%20answer.%20It%20is%20very%20surprising%20from%20both%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamson%20has%20repeatedly%20gotten%20out%20to%20short%20deliveries%20during%20the%20series%2C%20while%20Suryakumar's%20strength%20has%20been%20exploited%20into%20his%20weakness%2C%20as%20he%20has%20been%20dismissed%20playing%20his%20signature%20flick%20scoop%20shot%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSurya%20is%20a%20very%20experienced%20guy.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20the%20change%20of%20guard%20for%20Indian%20cricket%20in%20batting.%20But%20I%20think%20it's%20high%20time%20he%20changes%20his%20approach%20a%20little%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Samson%2C%20the%20mind%20will%20be%20playing%20tricks.%20If%20there%20are%20many%20questions%20in%20your%20head%2C%20it%20gets%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20advised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamson%20has%20tried%20different%20tactics%20to%20counter%20his%20short-ball%20weakness%2C%20including%20practising%20with%20a%20plastic%20ball%20and%20adopting%20a%20very%20different%20stance.%20But%20despite%20a%20couple%20of%20starts%2C%20Samson%20failed%20to%20score%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%20made%20just%2028%20runs%20in%20five%20innings%2C%20including%20two%20ducks%2C%20during%20the%20T20I%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738594500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fv6vd7ph8_suryakumar-yadav_625x300_03_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2025%2Fits-high-time-r-ashwins-brutal-analysis-of-suryakumar-yadav-sanju-samsons-poor-form-7625945%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20I